on-arrival: raiders_formed = 1

An Islamist paramilitary group associated with the MSP has been formed. Largely a youth and student movement, the raiders constitute another far right group, one even though is not as chauvinistic and nationalistic as the grey wolves, is still as reactionary as they are.
